[Cite as 06/12/2002 Case Announcements, 2002-Ohio-2625.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 12, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2002-0550. State v. Latham.

Coshocton App. No. 01CA1, 2001-0hio-1556. The discretionary appeal is allowed. Sua sponte, this cause is remanded to the court of appeals to consider the App.R. 26(B) application for reopening pursuant to S.Ct.Prac.R. II(2)(D)(1).

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
